# SauceLord Full-Stack Dashboard 🚀

A robust, full-stack project management and music archive application built to streamline creative workflows. This app allows users to track development tasks and manage a digital discography in real-time.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* **Frontend:** React.js (Hooks, Fetch API)
* **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js
* **Database:** PostgreSQL
* **Version Control:** Git & GitHub
* **Environment:** Dotenv for secure credential management

## ✨ Features

* **Project Tracker:** Full CRUD functionality (Create, Read, Update, Delete) for tasks.
* **Music Archive:** Specialized section to manage music releases, genres, and streaming links.
* **Real-time Filtering:** Search through music archives by genre instantly.
* **Interactive UI:** Status toggles with visual feedback (Checkmarks and strike-throughs).
* **Security:** Middleware implementation for CORS and environment variables to protect DB credentials.

